cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with deep learning algorithms for medical image analysis, specifically for diabetic retinopathy screening. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed solution also involves a generalization of the backpropagation method, which is a fundamental algorithm in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the potential of the proposed solution as an image mining tool, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
